    "body" : "<p>you could also create a class which extends <code>ArrayList</code>:</p>\n\n<p><code>public static class MyList extends ArrayList&lt;Myclass&gt; {}</code></p>\n\n<p>and then use it like: </p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;MyClass&gt; list = objectMapper.readValue(json, MyList.class);\n</code></pre>\n"
