      "body" : "Answer worked for me, and is clear and concise. Love it.  For me, I had a generic method that passed in a Class&lt;T&gt; myGenericClass and was able to do: List&lt;T&gt; list = mapper.readerForListOf(myGenericClass).readValue(json); Which worked nicely for my solution. Thanks again!"
